{
  "stem": "9728.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But on the way back, and I did not want to stay in Poland, I smuggled myself to the Czechoslovaki-- to the Czechoslovakia-- back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I stayed in Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I went back to Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I stayed a while still in Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Feldafing there was no problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, and you didn't have to do anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you got your food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you could get your bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, of course, we were 10, 12 people in a-- in a room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were just sleeping and eating.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you were free to do whatever you wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After-- and after being in Feldafing I decided that I want to move into-- to Munich.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went, and I rented a room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I rented.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, in Munich, the [INAUDIBLE] of the-- the people who supplied, they were very, very scarce.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you have to realize that Munich was all bombed out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were hardly any places to be gotten.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "However, to the Jewish committee, and to the German policy after the war, they forced people who were Nazis, and who still had some apartment, that they had to take in some people who looked for things.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was given a room at-- at some Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, assumingly they were Nazis.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Otherwise they wouldn't have forced them to take me in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They said, no, they were not Nazi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were what they called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The [GERMAN] was a German word for saying, well, I also ran.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, I ran with the crowd.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I was not a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "However--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I went back to Poland another time in 1946, because I did not want to give up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted to make sure that no one is alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
